{"type": "article", "id": 15618, "title": "《一日一果》", "description": null, "date": "1970-01-01T00:00:00Z", "super_tag": null, "tags": [], "category": null, "author": 4369, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 1, "image": "img/default_images/missing_article.png", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605195008AbFa3f7XJHcu012i.jpg\" title=\"木村宗慎\" alt=\"木村宗慎\" data-ratio=\"1.428125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><a href=\"http://www.amazon.cn/%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%80%E6%9E%9C-%E6%9C%A8%E6%9D%91%E5%AE%97%E6%85%8E/dp/B013QK10AO/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;qid=1443571292&amp;sr=8-1&amp;keywords=%E4%B8%80%E6%97%A5%E4%B8%80%E6%9E%9C\" target=\"_blank\">《一日一果》（日）木村宗慎 著</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t木村宗慎的《一日一果》，一本永远不必一口气读完的伴侣书：“待客的心意是最高的细节。本书里的每幅照片，于我都是一场盛会。”日子，果子，淡淡相映。读过很多美食书，多数只与美味有关，而这一本，实实在在与美学有关。孤芳自赏，从小老师就教育我们这是个贬义词，这本书，让你觉得，这四个字，一字不可易，绝对不是贬。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}